BrightBlade, Rage

* BrightBlade growled as she put her guns away and transformed to beast 
mode, she sighed and then looked over at Gangon.*

" Do we HAVE to go looking for Maximals? This is our chance to kick back and 
enjoy ourselves for a change, some time off."

* She sighed and relaxed her body a little as she sat and then looked away 
into the distance, she then looked at Gangon without turning her head. With 
a wink she said:*

" Besides, there's a lot better things to do then go hunting for Maximals."

* She smiled but then got up and began to trot off westward, it would be 
nice to actually not have to worry about Maximals for a mega-cycle or two.*

^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

* Rage nodded and began to follow Scourge, finally a chance at a meal!*
